Cryotek pointed at the debris that surrounded the craft. "Look, you
can tell from the data that it was only recently unearthed." Data
scrolled across the screen showing that a nearby volcano had errupted
in the past several weeks, creating shockwaves that revealed the
craft.

Smiling darkly Cryotek continued, "A trap from who, the Maximals? They
are on one continant and this one is on another, they are thousands of
miles away from it and it may be that It is too far away for them to
casually notice."

Cryotek paused for a moment, gazing thoughtfully at Hydras, "That
doen't mean that the Maximals won't find it eventually. It has a
definite small but detectable energy signature. If they get close
enough they will find it."
